# ER Diagram – Event Registration Portal

```text
+------------------+
|      USER        |
+------------------+
| user_id (PK)     |
| name             |
| email            |
| phone            |
| password         |
+------------------+
          |
          | Registers
          | 1:M
          v
+----------------------+
|    REGISTRATION      |
+----------------------+
| registration_id (PK) |
| user_id (FK)         |
| event_id (FK)        |
| registration_date    |
| status               |
+----------------------+
          ^
          |
          | M:1
          | For
          |
+------------------+
|      EVENT       |
+------------------+
| event_id (PK)    |
| event_name       |
| description      |
| date             |
| venue            |
| capacity         |
+------------------+
          ^
          |
          | Managed By
          | M:1
          |
+------------------+
|      ADMIN       |
+------------------+
| admin_id (PK)    |
| name             |
| email            |
| password         |
+------------------+

PK = Primary Key
FK = Foreign Key

Relationships:
1. One User can register for many Events.
2. One Event can have many Registrations.
3. One Admin can manage many Events.
```
